  "title": "ISic003081. Block containing section of civic accounts",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IXCSBXRM\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IXCSBXRM</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 1<br></span>  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΙΝΟΥ<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.</span>ΕΛΛ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">. 6.</span>]<span data-text=\"κόσια\">κόσια</span> τάλαντα [σ]ιτο[φυλάκοις] κυ̣α̣-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>μων λοιπὸν [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] τριάκοντα [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>σιτωνίῳ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φρύνιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φρύνιος\">Φρύνιος</span></span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]χίλια <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[ἑβ?]δομήκοντα [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] λοιπὸν [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>τάλαντα [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al10-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>ἐννέα ἑξήκοντα λίτραι [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al11-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al12-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al13-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>σιτωνίῳ [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al14-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] λοιπὸν <span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 2<br></span>  <br id=\"al1-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IXCSBXRM\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IXCSBXRM</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 1<br></span><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΙΝΟΥ<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·</span>ΕΛΛ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">······</span>]<span data-text=\"κόσια\">ΚΟΣΙΑ</span>ΤΑΛΑΝΤΑ[.]ΙΤΟ[........]Κ..<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΜΩΝΛΟΙΠΟΝ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΤΡΙΑΚΟΝΤΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΣΙΤΩΝΙΩ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φρύνιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φρύνιος\">ΦΡΥΝΙΟΣ</span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΧΙΛΙΑ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[..]ΔΟΜΗΚΟΝΤΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΛΟΙΠΟΝ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ΤΑΛΑΝΤΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al10-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>ΕΝΝΕΑΕΞΗΚΟΝΤΑΛΙΤΡΑΙ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al11-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al12-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al13-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>ΣΙΤΩΝΙΩ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al14-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΛΟΙΠΟΝ<span class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 2<br></span><br id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003081_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2009-10-06\" src=\"ISic003081_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003081.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2009-10-06\" src=\"ISic003081-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Manganaro 1988</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The text belongs to the older (C2 or early C1 BCE) series of account inscriptions. The surviving state of the stone makes it extremely difficult to read, and although some more letters are visible, Manganaro chose not to present them and fresh autopsy is required.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 38.0973a <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Manganaro 1988 155-156 fig.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001832\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001832</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
